description: Department of Fiscal Policy - Order to impose and charge Excise Duty on Import/Local Supply of Spirits (Ethyl Alcohal), to impose Excise Duty on Malt Liquor ; to Levy Excise Duty on Country made Foreign Spirits manufactured in Sri Lanka and on Molasses, Palmyrah, Coconut and Processed Arrack with effect from 10.10.2014
